<Defs>
  <XenotypeDef>
    <defName>GegeXT_VanDrelahr</defName>
    <label>Van Drelahr</label>
    <description>This xenotype was engineered to thrive in hostile worlds where most beings fail.
Their bodies combine physical resilience, accelerated learning, and remarkable adaptability, the result of advanced archogenetic design focused on long-term survival rather than raw, short-term power.

They possess sharpened senses, improved reflexes, and a mind inclined toward analysis, planning, and constant self-improvement. They are neither simple soldiers nor ordinary colonists; instead, they are meant to be the backbone of a colony, capable of learning quickly, working efficiently, and enduring extreme conditions without breaking easily.

Despite their advantages, they are not emotionless constructs. They retain curiosity, emotional depth, and a strong instinct to protect what they consider their own—be it a community, a project, or an ideal. Their genetics favor intelligent cooperation and sustained growth, making them an ideal choice for ambitious colonies that seek to endure beyond a single generation.

In the wrong hands, they can become an unrelenting force.
In the right hands, they are the foundation of a civilization that refuses to disappear.</description>
    <descriptionShort>Genetically enhanced humans designed for adaptability, rapid learning, and long-term survival in extreme environments.</descriptionShort>
    <iconPath>UI/Icons/Xenotypes/Custom/Yttakin_4</iconPath>
